==Description==
The '''Cyan Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]] first encountered in [[Alola]].

==Details==
The Cyan Shard can be used, alongside [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}}, to purchase items at the [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Cyan Shard appears in the Underground as a 4x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:CyanShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
Cyan Shards can be used together with other [[Shards]] to purchase the following items:
{| class="wikitable" style="text-align: center;"
|-
! Item Name !! Shards !! Quest Points
|-
| [[File:Ice_Stone.png|20px]] [[Ice Stone]] || 50 [[File:Blue_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] [[Blue Shard|Blue Shards]] <br> 75 [[File:Cyan_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] Cyan Shards || 625 {{Questpoints}}
|}

For details as to where one can purchase these items, please check the [[Shard Trader]] page for more information.

==Acquisition==
Cyan Shards can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

